Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.11,0:00:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone, Kaleido Star is about to start!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.06,0:00:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When watching Kaleido Star,\Nplease keep the room brightly lit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.81,0:00:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and sit as far from the TV as you can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm Sora Naegino.\NI came to America all by myself{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.74,0:00:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}with aspirations of joining Kaleido Stage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.25,0:00:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everything is new to me, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.17,0:00:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I'm doing my best in the spirit\Nof "try it rather than think about it."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.68,0:00:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's nothing I can't do if I try,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.93,0:00:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and if I can do it without\Ntrying, I'll be super lucky.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.73,0:00:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And if I'm gonna do it, I just\Ngotta do it! Gotta! Gotta! That's me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.93,0:00:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, well, well, if you were the\Nonly one not given anything to do,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.06,0:00:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}you'd get really depressed, too, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.06,0:00:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It makes you sad, and you want to cry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.98,0:00:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This time, I'm the only\None who doesn't get a role.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.54,0:01:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder what it is that\NI can do? I wonder? I wonder?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.05,0:01:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is it that you want to do? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.65,0:01:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time I was asked that {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.50,0:01:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I looked up at the blue sky {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.29,0:01:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The answer is only in my heart {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.59,0:01:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't easily say the\Nwords that are really important{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.12,0:01:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I start running towards\Nthe place the light points to{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's so much in my heart\Nthat I want to embrace, I could cry{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.32,0:02:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll keep painting my way,\NI promise, take it someday{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Beyond the horizon,\Nwhere the white clouds drift{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The future is lined up and\Nit'll always be there by my side{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.53,0:02:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The Amazing Distant Stage."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.42,0:03:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You're wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.21,0:03:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I missed it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your spins are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.47,0:03:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.57,0:03:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can all Asians do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.59,0:03:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Oh, it's because\NI used to do rhythmic gymnastics.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.06,0:03:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.27,0:03:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.43,0:03:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the show that Miss Layla and the\Nothers were practicing was Cinderella.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.60,0:03:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Even all trainees\Nare supposed to appear in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.70,0:03:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.64,0:03:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. So good luck, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:04:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just want to wish\NSora luck, don't you, Ken?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.37,0:04:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cinderella...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.13,0:04:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! I need to tell my \Nfamily about this quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad, mom, and grandma\Nare all big fans of Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm their star of hope, they'll\Nbe happy to hear that I'll be on stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if my role is just to play the pumpkin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.67,0:04:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I'd guess that\Nyou're more of the prince type.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.83,0:04:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, actually I'd rather play the pumpkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.89,0:04:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's because my\Nfather's a stand-up comedian.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.43,0:04:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that's why. Sora,\Nwhat about your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My family...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They weren't very enthusiastic\Nabout you joining Kaleido Stage, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.45,0:04:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... By the way, aren't you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.32,0:04:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry and go to the dining hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.83,0:04:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.29,0:04:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here he is again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you?! I am the Spirit of the Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.13,0:04:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not talk of me as if I am a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:04:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.24,0:04:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only people who are\Nchosen for the stage can see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.97,0:05:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear only certain people \Ncan see ghosts too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.56,0:05:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh! Are you saying\Nthat you cannot trust me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.08,0:05:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.62,0:05:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shocking! Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.19,0:05:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to know why I am here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're waiting for a chance\Nto peep at me in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.22,0:05:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am searching for the one who will be able
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.66,0:05:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to perform the legendary great maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.93,0:05:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The legendary great maneuver?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.94,0:05:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.83,0:05:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a maneuver that was\Nperformed only once a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For those who cannot see me, the\Nmaneuver would be utterly impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.96,0:05:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of maneuver is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.88,0:05:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.32,0:05:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are truly the chosen one,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.69,0:05:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will be possessed by the charm\Nof the maneuver as soon as you hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.64,0:05:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, even though you are not skilled enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will want to perform it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.59,0:05:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will recklessly attempt \Nit and die trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.32,0:05:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone who's tried that\Nmaneuver without the proper skills
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.34,0:06:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,has failed to execute the maneuver and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.98,0:06:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.64,0:06:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If what you said is true,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you should be showing\Nup at Miss Layla's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.11,0:06:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I said, someone who cannot see me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought, your purpose\Nis to peep at me bathing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.19,0:06:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that were my purpose,\NI would rather go to Layla's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.66,0:06:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems we have just proven\Nthat I have been telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.29,0:06:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate it that I can't come\Nup with a counterargument.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.82,0:06:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, please gather around!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.25,0:06:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, Boss has an announcement\Nabout the cast for Cinderella.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may know this already,\Nbut the upcoming Cinderella
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.93,0:06:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is a masterpiece that\Nincludes a ballroom dance scene,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.37,0:06:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so all of you will be \Nappearing in it as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.14,0:06:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will now announce the roles.\NFirst, castle guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.61,0:06:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Albert.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.36,0:06:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Emilio.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.95,0:06:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.61,0:06:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.32,0:06:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:06:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You three, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.61,0:07:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Town girls. Clair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.18,0:07:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeanne.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.53,0:07:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Prince's attendant, Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.37,0:07:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! It's perfect. Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You get to perform with Mr. Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.35,0:07:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The character won't have any gags...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.33,0:07:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, nope, it won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.09,0:07:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the role of the fairy godmother,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want several of you to practice the\Nrole first before I make the selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you are not chosen,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.69,0:07:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll be part of the crowd scene,\Nso do not let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.54,0:07:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here are the candidates\Nfor the fairy godmother role:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.16,0:07:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Charlotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.33,0:07:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Julie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.62,0:07:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.65,0:07:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.40,0:07:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mia!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.53,0:07:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.36,0:07:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Glad it's a role you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.55,0:07:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's great. So great! You're amazing, Mia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.16,0:07:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best and win the role.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.93,0:07:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm gonna do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.14,0:07:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the crowd in the\Nballroom dance scene, Kevin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.57,0:07:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.46,0:07:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Joseph.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.25,0:07:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mileyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.55,0:07:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I... I wonder which role I'll play.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:07:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monica.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.11,0:07:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.85,0:07:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.34,0:08:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He didn't call my name. Just my name.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be some kind of mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.53,0:08:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he just forgot to call your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.10,0:08:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, excuse me, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.97,0:08:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is my role?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have a role.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.28,0:08:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have... a role?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.83,0:08:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.29,0:08:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a role you can \Nstart playing tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The role is to hand out toys to\Nthe children during intermission.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.00,0:08:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toys?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.75,0:08:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you call it a role if the\Nperson isn't even on stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.86,0:08:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't like it, you don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.91,0:08:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it. I'll play the role!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like just for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, a perfect match!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's practice together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Let's do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.44,0:08:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mia, Anna...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.50,0:09:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have time for practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.05,0:09:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting tomorrow, you have to\Nplay the role of passing out toys.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.09,0:09:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, everyone! Please\Ncome get the scripts here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss is such a jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.83,0:09:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Since it's come to this,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we should drop a frog down his back,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or shave off half of his\Nbeard while he's sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.08,0:09:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's shave off half of his\Neyebrows and hair, too, while we're at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.17,0:09:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about drawing eyes on his glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.81,0:09:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it be better to draw\Nthe glasses on his eyes instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.90,0:09:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for worrying about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.66,0:09:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.23,0:09:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know both of you really\Nwant to read the script, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me,\Nyou can go back to your rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.45,0:09:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.42,0:09:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.38,0:09:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a person "chosen for the stage"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.57,0:09:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be some kind of mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.29,0:10:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told him I'd do it on the\Nspur of the moment, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.15,0:10:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone else is practicing for Cinderella.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.84,0:10:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.21,0:10:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.84,0:10:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you handing those out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.69,0:10:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss told me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't look happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.28,0:10:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was told that this was\Nthe only role available for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.63,0:10:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a long way to go if\Nyou're still saying things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.27,0:10:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora! It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.79,0:10:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Intermission is in three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Boss has something in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.30,0:11:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Boss doesn't like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.92,0:11:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just the other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.44,0:11:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got into that situation \Nwith Miss Layla, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.03,0:11:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, everyone! Attention please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, attention please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.88,0:11:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking you all, please listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in my way! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.97,0:11:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy! My ice cream!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.03,0:11:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.97,0:11:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Policeman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.18,0:11:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off duty today, so I came to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you're having trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.14,0:12:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey{\i0}! Listen to what my \Nfriend Sora has to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.13,0:12:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't hand out all\Nof it during intermission.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.37,0:12:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you would do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.35,0:12:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you can't even fill a role like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.90,0:12:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never should have made\Nan exception to accept you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare he talk to me like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.64,0:12:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How does he expect me to hand\Nout all of it in such a short time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.78,0:12:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be having fun,\Nasking me to do the impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.01,0:12:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla is shining on the stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while I'm off the stage...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.96,0:13:01.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Jump Kick"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.27,0:13:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, why don't you give it a try, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.12,0:13:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the best way to relieve stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:08.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Jump Kick"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must've been tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.58,0:13:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dinner's delicious today, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.84,0:13:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Even the fries are \Nmore crisp than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.65,0:13:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to tiptoe around me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, how was the Cinderella practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it was tough as expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.49,0:13:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of stage is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the last ballroom dance\Nscene, Miss Layla and Mr. Yuri
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.07,0:13:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are supposed to leap on six trapezes\None after another as if they're dancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that's amazing.\NWhat about everything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.22,0:14:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are not in the mood to do anything.\NYou are not motivated.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.76,0:14:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother telling my fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.39,0:14:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, it's pretty obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.80,0:14:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is also the card that governs creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The road is blocked. But if you\Nwant to see what is up ahead,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.45,0:14:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you have to create your own road.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.45,0:14:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "my own road"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.46,0:14:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.82,0:14:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.46,0:14:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.53,0:14:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really going to \Ndo it in a clown suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. If I can't appear on stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.18,0:14:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just turn the seating\Narea into my own stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.60,0:14:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn the seating area into your own stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.09,0:14:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's great that you always have\Nthis positive attitude, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez. Ken, you're still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.30,0:15:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Oh, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'm all set!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.28,0:15:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.56,0:15:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you enjoying Kaleido Stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.47,0:15:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, my friends, everyone\Nwho wants a light, gather around!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should hurry, or\Nelse the show will start soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.89,0:15:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.69,0:15:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Here. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.03,0:15:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.91,0:15:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finished handing it all out today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.99,0:16:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no comprehension\Nof how the show is run.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.66,0:16:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you talking about this costume?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.12,0:16:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.46,0:16:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think seriously about what your role is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.08,0:16:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?! I don't understand at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.51,0:16:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.34,0:16:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The show was delayed\Nten minutes because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.72,0:16:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You put on a pretty flashy performance,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.40,0:16:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it took a long time\Nto calm down the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.65,0:16:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you asked the kids to\Ncome out to get the lights, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.59,0:16:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some of them couldn't find\Ntheir way back to their seats,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.60,0:16:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and some were in such a\Nhurry that they tripped and fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.92,0:16:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.54,0:16:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was only thinking about\Ngetting attention for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.67,0:16:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only cared about getting\Npeople to say that I was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:16:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't thinking about the\Nprogression of the show at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.67,0:17:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder Boss is mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh! Mr. Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.56,0:17:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.79,0:17:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to see a clown cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if your heart is crying, isn't it\Na clown's job to make people happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.65,0:17:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you looking like that, Ken?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.08,0:17:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you hand out the lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.62,0:17:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, anything for you, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.02,0:17:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll be fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because I finally understand what my role is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.36,0:17:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A clown's job is to make people happy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.24,0:18:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.02,0:18:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.90,0:18:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That clown's been standing \Nthere all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.39,0:18:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.74,0:18:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks fun. How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.67,0:18:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.09,0:18:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe she's \Nperforming in the lobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.79,0:18:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.96,0:18:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.93,0:18:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The show has already started.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I'm not on stage, I'm still\Ngoing to completely play my role.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's the clown I saw earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wasn't a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I'm here to give everyone a magic wand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.47,0:19:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, use your power to\Nfill the night sky with stars, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.30,0:19:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't have a lead role\Nor anything like that,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.60,0:19:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but if I can bring even \Njust a little enjoyment{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.14,0:19:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to everyone as a supporting character...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.36,0:19:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I haven't finished yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.38,0:19:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I understand a little now. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.79,0:19:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All roles exist for the audience.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.00,0:19:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bringing these smiles to their\Nfaces. That is Kaleido Stage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.99,0:20:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.67,0:20:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.46,0:20:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.10,0:20:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.46,0:20:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure you want me to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.89,0:20:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An autograph... let me think,\Nhow should I sign it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.66,0:20:45.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Sora"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.95,0:20:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.05,0:20:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.22,0:20:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all. I'm the one\Nwho should be thanking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.33,0:21:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tim, we're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.17,0:21:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.27,0:21:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.99,0:21:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, you did a good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.95,0:21:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I signed an autograph for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.01,0:21:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be nice if the boy\Ncherished your autograph forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.51,0:21:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.15,0:21:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kalos.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.94,0:21:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what you're expecting from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.82,0:21:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.01,0:21:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your autograph is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.62,0:21:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.32,0:21:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, there are a lot\Nof things you need to practice
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.37,0:21:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before you practice your autograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.06,0:21:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.79,0:22:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I feel like I understand a\Nlittle bit of what you said, Fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.29,0:22:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Creating my own road\Nmeans creating my own role.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.35,0:22:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And waiting for me ahead on\Nthat road is the audience's smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.34,0:22:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you thanking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.49,0:22:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.91,0:22:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, keep that thought in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.84,0:22:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, go take a bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.69,0:22:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.99,0:22:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, stop blindfolding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.27,0:22:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.94,0:22:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ungrateful wretch!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.23,0:22:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you're lonely, what do you do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.91,0:22:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Never say you don't get any of that{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.25,0:22:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sleep, play, flip through a magazine{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.10,0:22:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you're lonely, you're lonely{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.55,0:22:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like always, invisible vibes fly\Naround the city today, tulututu{\i0}*
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.30,0:22:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anyway, the vector of my heart\Nis talking about so many reasons{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.81,0:23:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to be free and fly the skies{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.65,0:23:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I don't have space to spread my wings{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.38,0:23:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I have faith {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.42,0:23:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is a future yet to be shaped{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.16,0:23:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And there's a me that I want to shape{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.84,0:23:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if I'm sad, even if it's a mistake{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.30,0:23:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll do what I want and\Nfly towards the freedom{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.68,0:23:36.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Next Kaleido Star"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.68,0:23:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't want people like you\Ngetting up on the trampoline!{\i0}
